{"tid":1856632,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全世界同我入嚟做一樣嘢","createTime":"2020-02-01T17:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T14:40:04.000Z","uid":224657,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"daca2a267adbbe76115f02afec728edad0e36ece","tid":1856632,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:26:15.000Z","msg":"report爆呢個叫偽韓妹嘅page！report到佢摺為止！！！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6O30tO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6O30tO.jpg&h=26f1bbe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事緣係咁的<br />\n尋日黃大仙有間叫樂文文具嘅黃店先以20蚊，後來因為來貨關係改做25蚊，賣kf94口罩(醫護人員同孕婦一律100蚊6個)<br />\n唔知樂文係乜嘅人可以啲facebook search樂文文具公司。<br />\n一間黃到發金由6月開始已經幫緊手足嘅店嚟。<br />\n<br />\n依家樂文比呢條臭閪偽韓妹話食人血饅頭<br />\n佢聲稱自己可以以8蚊入到一個kf94但係到依家未入到香港嘅，然後就屌樂文食人血饅頭。<br />\n<br />\n有唔少人入去理論，當中包括樓豬我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後呢條臭閪就封鎖曬不利自己嘅人嘅留言<br />\n有留言拆穿咗佢同白影有來往，簡單嚟講算係私怨po嚟<br />\n<br />\n我上一個po都有唔少巴絲留言話樂文好幫手足，絕對唔係呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />25蚊個kf94都完全合理。<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家一人一個report report到條臭閪page摺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38d2f4fb7471f618bb25132e028fed5252ef7d1","tid":1856632,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1313d0cf088506676e013264fd8687ca5b51d9b0","tid":1856632,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"611421da79651b2b0019aa582143ac0f695506b2","tid":1856632,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T17:27:03.000Z","msg":"[警世]林鄭政府唔肯封關同插手口罩短缺問題背後既計算<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1855771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1855771</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ee068b5b587277d683f211e4d4a54867421e463","tid":1856632,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"